metadata.title: Recreation Point Features - CNF

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest

metadata.description: Data Type: Recreation;  Recreation point features with recreation site name and feature type, including boat ramp, cabin, campground, historical site, special use permit, trailhead and viewing point. Also indicates if there is existing or potential use.
